    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最低大概四千，最高能到一万一左右。另外我希望能同时用bar和line两种形式展示同一组数据，bar看具体数值，line看趋势走向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "bar",
        "line",
        "y-axis"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，y轴范围设为4000到11000。x轴月份按jan到dec排列。现在我来输入具体的revenue数据，您确认一下：一月5000，二月6000，三月7500，四月8200，五月9500，六月10500，七月11000，八月10200，九月9200，十月8500，十一月7000，十二月6000。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "x-axis",
        "y-axis",
        "bar",
        "line",
        "jan"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "数据没问题，七月是全年peak，之后逐月回落。bar和line都用这同一组数据对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "bar",
        "line"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "对，同一组数据。我现在生成图表，bar显示每个月的in $数值，line连接各点展示趋势。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "bar",
        "line"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
